---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import '../styles/global.css';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy - FRNDSAPP" description="FRNDSAPP Privacy Policy. We literally CANNOT see your data. This is by design, not policy.">
  <section class="pt-32 pb-20">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <!-- Header -->
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h1 class="section-heading mb-4">
          <span class="gradient-text">Privacy Policy</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-text-secondary">Last Updated: January 2026</p>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Intro -->
      <div class="glass-card p-6 md:p-8 mb-12 border-l-4 border-primary">
        <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-xl mb-4">Our Privacy Promise</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-accent italic mb-4">"We literally CANNOT see your data. This is by design, not policy."</p>
        <p class="text-text-secondary">
          Unlike other apps that promise privacy but hold your data, FRNDSAPP is architecturally designed so that we CANNOT access your private information ‚Äî even if we wanted to, even if compelled.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Content -->
      <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none space-y-12">
        
        <!-- Section 1 -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-2xl mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-primary/20 flex items-center justify-center text-lg">1</span>
            What We Collect (Minimal)
          </h2>
          
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div class="glass-card p-5">
              <h3 class="font-display font-semibold text-lg mb-3">Account Information</h3>
              <ul class="text-text-secondary space-y-2">
                <li>‚Ä¢ Email or phone number (for authentication only)</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ Your chosen display name</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ Profile pictures (verified against your face)</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="glass-card p-5">
              <h3 class="font-display font-semibold text-lg mb-3">Verification Data</h3>
              <ul class="text-text-secondary space-y-2">
                <li>‚Ä¢ 3D face liveness scan (stored securely, used ONLY for verification)</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ This ensures no fake accounts and validates your profile pictures</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="glass-card p-5">
              <h3 class="font-display font-semibold text-lg mb-3">Space Participation</h3>
              <ul class="text-text-secondary space-y-2">
                <li>‚Ä¢ Which Spaces you join</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ Your public profile in those Spaces</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ Your matching preferences (used for AI matching)</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="glass-card p-5">
              <h3 class="font-display font-semibold text-lg mb-3">Location (Optional, Privacy-Preserved)</h3>
              <ul class="text-text-secondary space-y-2">
                <li>‚Ä¢ Approximate area for nearby matching (geohash, not exact coordinates)</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ We show "3.2 km away" ‚Äî NEVER your exact location</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ You control when to share location</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>
        
        <!-- Section 2 -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-2xl mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-green-500/20 flex items-center justify-center text-lg">2</span>
            What We CANNOT See (By Design)
          </h2>
          
          <div class="glass-card p-6 border border-green-500/30">
            <h3 class="font-display font-semibold text-lg mb-4 text-green-400">End-to-End Encrypted Content</h3>
            <p class="text-text-secondary mb-4">
              ALL of the following are encrypted on YOUR device and can ONLY be decrypted by the intended recipient:
            </p>
            <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3">
              {[
                'Text messages ‚Äî We see encrypted blobs only',
                'Photos you share ‚Äî Encrypted before upload',
                'Videos you share ‚Äî Encrypted before upload',
                'Files & documents ‚Äî Encrypted before upload',
                'Voice messages ‚Äî Encrypted before upload',
                'Location sharing ‚Äî Encrypted coordinates',
                'Audio calls ‚Äî WebRTC E2EE, we never hear',
                'Video calls ‚Äî WebRTC E2EE, we never see',
              ].map((item) => (
                <div class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <span class="text-green-400">‚úì</span>
                  <span class="text-text-secondary text-sm">{item}</span>
                </div>
              ))}
            </div>
            <p class="text-accent mt-4 text-sm">
              We use the Signal Protocol ‚Äî the same encryption trusted by journalists, activists, and security professionals worldwide.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="glass-card p-6 mt-6 border border-purple-500/30">
            <h3 class="font-display font-semibold text-lg mb-3 text-purple-400">OTS (One-Time Secure) Messages</h3>
            <p class="text-text-secondary">These are EXTRA secure:</p>
            <ul class="text-text-secondary mt-2 space-y-1 text-sm">
              <li>‚Ä¢ Encrypted end-to-end</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Camera verifies recipient in real-time</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Auto-delete after viewing</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ We have ZERO access to content</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </section>
        
        <!-- Section 3 -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-2xl mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-cyan-500/20 flex items-center justify-center text-lg">3</span>
            Contact Sync ‚Äî Hash Only
          </h2>
          
          <div class="glass-card p-6 bg-dark-surface/50">
            <h3 class="font-display font-semibold text-lg mb-4">How Contact Sync Works</h3>
            <div class="space-y-3">
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-primary/30 flex items-center justify-center text-xs">1</span>
                <span class="text-text-secondary">Your phone hashes each contact (one-way encryption)</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-primary/30 flex items-center justify-center text-xs">2</span>
                <span class="text-text-secondary">Only hash values are sent to our servers</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-primary/30 flex items-center justify-center text-xs">3</span>
                <span class="text-text-secondary">We compare hashes with registered user hashes</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-primary/30 flex items-center justify-center text-xs">4</span>
                <span class="text-text-secondary">We return: "These hashes match existing users"</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-primary/30 flex items-center justify-center text-xs">5</span>
                <span class="text-text-secondary">Your app shows: "These contacts are on FRNDSAPP"</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-4 p-3 bg-accent/10 rounded-lg">
              <p class="text-accent text-sm font-medium">RESULT: We NEVER see names, numbers, or any contact info. We literally cannot extract your contact list from hashes.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>
        
        <!-- Section 4 -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-2xl mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-green-500/20 flex items-center justify-center text-lg">4</span>
            3D Face Verification
          </h2>
          
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
            <div class="glass-card p-5">
              <h3 class="font-display font-semibold text-lg mb-3">Why We Do It</h3>
              <ul class="text-text-secondary space-y-2 text-sm">
                <li>‚Ä¢ Ensures every user is a real human</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ Prevents fake profiles and catfishing</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ Validates that profile pictures are actually YOU</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="glass-card p-5">
              <h3 class="font-display font-semibold text-lg mb-3">How It Works</h3>
              <ul class="text-text-secondary space-y-2 text-sm">
                <li>‚Ä¢ One-time 3D liveness scan at registration</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ Checks: depth, movement, blink, anti-spoofing</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ No photos of photos, no masks, no screens</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ Stored securely, used ONLY for verification</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="glass-card p-5 mt-6">
            <h3 class="font-display font-semibold text-lg mb-3">Profile Picture Verification</h3>
            <ul class="text-text-secondary space-y-2 text-sm">
              <li>‚Ä¢ Every profile pic is compared to your verified face</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ If the face doesn't match, the picture is rejected</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ This prevents catfishing and fake photos</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </section>
        
        <!-- Section 5 -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-2xl mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-teal-500/20 flex items-center justify-center text-lg">5</span>
            Location Privacy
          </h2>
          
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
            <div class="glass-card p-5">
              <h3 class="font-display font-semibold text-lg mb-3">What We Know</h3>
              <ul class="text-text-secondary space-y-2 text-sm">
                <li>‚Ä¢ Approximate area (geohash) for nearby matching</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ Example: "Downtown Seattle area" ‚Äî NOT your address</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="glass-card p-5">
              <h3 class="font-display font-semibold text-lg mb-3">What We Show Others</h3>
              <ul class="text-text-secondary space-y-2 text-sm">
                <li>‚Ä¢ Distance only: "3.2 km away"</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ NEVER your exact coordinates</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ NEVER your address or precise location</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="glass-card p-5">
              <h3 class="font-display font-semibold text-lg mb-3">You Control It</h3>
              <ul class="text-text-secondary space-y-2 text-sm">
                <li>‚Ä¢ Location sharing is optional</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ You can disable it anytime</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ Spaces work without location too</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>
        
        <!-- Section 6 -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-2xl mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-blue-500/20 flex items-center justify-center text-lg">6</span>
            Data Storage & Security
          </h2>
          
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
            <div class="glass-card p-5">
              <h3 class="font-display font-semibold text-lg mb-3">Where Data Lives</h3>
              <ul class="text-text-secondary space-y-2 text-sm">
                <li>‚Ä¢ Encrypted messages: On your device + encrypted backup</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ Account data: Secure cloud infrastructure</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ Face verification: Encrypted, isolated storage</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="glass-card p-5">
              <h3 class="font-display font-semibold text-lg mb-3">Security Measures</h3>
              <ul class="text-text-secondary space-y-2 text-sm">
                <li>‚Ä¢ All data encrypted at rest</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ TLS encryption in transit</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ Regular security audits</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ No third-party analytics that track you</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>
        
        <!-- Section 7 -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-2xl mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-red-500/20 flex items-center justify-center text-lg">7</span>
            What We DON'T Do
          </h2>
          
          <div class="glass-card p-6">
            <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
              {[
                'We don\'t sell your data ‚Äî We have nothing to sell',
                'We don\'t show targeted ads ‚Äî We can\'t, we don\'t have your data',
                'We don\'t read your messages ‚Äî We literally cannot',
                'We don\'t share with third parties ‚Äî Nothing to share',
                'We don\'t mine your contacts ‚Äî We only see hashes',
                'We don\'t track your location history ‚Äî Only current for matching',
                'We don\'t store message content ‚Äî It\'s E2EE, we only see blobs',
              ].map((item) => (
                <div class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <span class="text-red-400">‚ùå</span>
                  <span class="text-text-secondary text-sm">{item}</span>
                </div>
              ))}
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>
        
        <!-- Section 8 -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-2xl mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-primary/20 flex items-center justify-center text-lg">8</span>
            Your Rights
          </h2>
          
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
            <div class="glass-card p-5">
              <h3 class="font-display font-semibold text-lg mb-3">Access Your Data</h3>
              <ul class="text-text-secondary space-y-2 text-sm">
                <li>‚Ä¢ Export your account information anytime</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ See which Spaces you're in</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ View your profile data</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="glass-card p-5">
              <h3 class="font-display font-semibold text-lg mb-3">Delete Your Data</h3>
              <ul class="text-text-secondary space-y-2 text-sm">
                <li>‚Ä¢ Delete your account completely</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ All your data is removed</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ Messages you sent remain encrypted (others keep their copy)</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="glass-card p-5">
              <h3 class="font-display font-semibold text-lg mb-3">Control Your Privacy</h3>
              <ul class="text-text-secondary space-y-2 text-sm">
                <li>‚Ä¢ Adjust location sharing</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ Control who can message you</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ Block users instantly</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>
        
        <!-- Section 9 -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-2xl mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-orange-500/20 flex items-center justify-center text-lg">9</span>
            Open Source Transparency
          </h2>
          
          <div class="glass-card p-6">
            <p class="text-text-secondary mb-4">Our frontend code is fully open source:</p>
            <ul class="text-text-secondary space-y-2 text-sm mb-6">
              <li>‚Ä¢ GitHub: <a href="https://github.com/frndsapp" class="text-accent hover:underline">github.com/frndsapp</a></li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Audit our encryption implementation</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Verify our privacy claims</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Report security issues</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="text-xl text-accent italic">"Don't trust us ‚Äî VERIFY us."</p>
          </div>
        </section>
        
        <!-- Section 10 -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-2xl mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-purple-500/20 flex items-center justify-center text-lg">10</span>
            OTS Messages ‚Äî Extra Privacy
          </h2>
          
          <div class="glass-card p-6 border border-purple-500/30">
            <h3 class="font-display font-semibold text-lg mb-4 text-purple-400">OTS Message Privacy</h3>
            <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
              {[
                { icon: 'üì∑', text: 'Camera activates to verify recipient' },
                { icon: 'üë§', text: 'Only YOUR verified face can unlock' },
                { icon: 'üö´', text: 'Blocks if you look away or move' },
                { icon: '‚ö†Ô∏è', text: 'Deletes if anyone else appears' },
                { icon: 'üì±', text: 'Works only on primary device' },
                { icon: 'üì∏', text: 'Gray patterns blur screenshot attempts' },
                { icon: 'üîî', text: 'Sender notified if screenshot detected' },
                { icon: 'üí®', text: 'Auto-deletes after viewing' },
              ].map((item) => (
                <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <span class="text-xl">{item.icon}</span>
                  <span class="text-text-secondary text-sm">{item.text}</span>
                </div>
              ))}
            </div>
            <div class="mt-6 p-3 bg-purple-500/10 rounded-lg">
              <p class="text-purple-400 text-sm font-medium">RESULT: The most private way to share sensitive information.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>
        
        <!-- Section 11 -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-2xl mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-yellow-500/20 flex items-center justify-center text-lg">11</span>
            Children's Privacy
          </h2>
          
          <div class="glass-card p-5">
            <p class="text-text-secondary">
              FRNDSAPP is not intended for users under 18. 3D face verification helps ensure age-appropriate usage.
            </p>
          </div>
        </section>
        
        <!-- Section 12 -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-2xl mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-primary/20 flex items-center justify-center text-lg">12</span>
            Changes to This Policy
          </h2>
          
          <div class="glass-card p-5">
            <p class="text-text-secondary mb-3">We'll notify you of significant changes via:</p>
            <ul class="text-text-secondary space-y-2 text-sm">
              <li>‚Ä¢ In-app notification</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Email (if provided)</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </section>
        
        <!-- Section 13 -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-2xl mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-accent/20 flex items-center justify-center text-lg">13</span>
            Contact Us
          </h2>
          
          <div class="glass-card p-5">
            <p class="text-text-secondary mb-3">Questions about privacy?</p>
            <ul class="text-text-secondary space-y-2">
              <li>‚Ä¢ Email: <a href="mailto:privacy@frndsapp.com" class="text-accent hover:underline">privacy@frndsapp.com</a></li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ GitHub Issues: For security researchers</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </section>
        
        <!-- Summary -->
        <section class="mt-16">
          <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-2xl mb-6 text-center">
            <span class="gradient-text">Summary: The FRNDSAPP Privacy Difference</span>
          </h2>
          
          <div class="glass-card p-6 overflow-x-auto">
            <table class="w-full text-sm">
              <thead>
                <tr class="border-b border-white/10">
                  <th class="text-left py-3 px-4 text-red-400">What Others Do</th>
                  <th class="text-left py-3 px-4 text-green-400">What FRNDSAPP Does</th>
                </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody class="text-text-secondary">
                <tr class="border-b border-white/5">
                  <td class="py-3 px-4">Store your messages</td>
                  <td class="py-3 px-4">Can't read them (E2EE)</td>
                </tr>
                <tr class="border-b border-white/5">
                  <td class="py-3 px-4">See your contacts</td>
                  <td class="py-3 px-4">Only see hashes</td>
                </tr>
                <tr class="border-b border-white/5">
                  <td class="py-3 px-4">Track exact location</td>
                  <td class="py-3 px-4">Only approximate area</td>
                </tr>
                <tr class="border-b border-white/5">
                  <td class="py-3 px-4">Allow fake profiles</td>
                  <td class="py-3 px-4">3D face verified only</td>
                </tr>
                <tr class="border-b border-white/5">
                  <td class="py-3 px-4">Sell your data</td>
                  <td class="py-3 px-4">Have nothing to sell</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td class="py-3 px-4">Promise privacy</td>
                  <td class="py-3 px-4">Prove it with open source</td>
                </tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
          
          <p class="text-center text-xl text-accent italic mt-8">"Privacy isn't our policy. It's our architecture."</p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
